HORROR:Kolchak-The Night Stalker, Monsters, The Outer Limits
       Tales From The Darkside, Twilight Zone

SCIENCE FICTION:Automan, Battlestar Galactica, Blake's 7, Dr. Who 1,
                Dr. Who 2, Logan's Run, Otherworld, Planet Of The Apes,
                Something Is Out There, Space 1999, Star Trek (TOS), 
                Time Tunnel, UFO (1), UFO (2), V, War Of The Worlds, X-Files

COMEDY:Fawlty Towers, Max Headroom, Monty Python's Flying Circus, 
       Red Dwarf (1), Red Dwarf (2), Young Ones

ADVENTURE:Adventures Of Brisco County Jr. (1), Adventures Of Brisco County
          Jr. (2), Amazing Spiderman, Batman, Invisible Man, Land Of The
          Lost, Lois And Clark, Wizards And Warriors

ANIMATION:Batman-TAS (1), Batman-TAS (2), Johnny Quest, Supercar, 
          Thunderbirds

