SEASON:     1
EPISODE:    1
TITLE:      The End
AIR DATE:   2/15/1987

SYNOPSIS:

The Red Dwarf is mining around the moons  of Saturn.   Five  miles long and
three miles wide, the ship has a crew of 169.  Within 24 hours, 168 of them
will be dead.

