Lister contracts a mutated form of pneumonia, and  has hallucinations which
become real.  Two of  his mental  characteristics form  into actual beings.
His confidence (who looks  like the  stereotypical U.S.   sports announcer)
wants him  to  take  charge,   but  his   paranoia  (who   looks  like  the
