6/25/92                  RED DWARF GUIDE (season 2)               OTTO HEUER/10
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

SEASON:     2
EPISODE:    7
TITLE:      Kryten
AIR DATE:   9/6/1988

SYNOPSIS:

The Red Dwarf picks up a distress call from  another space  ship which says
three female  officers  have  been  injured.    To  their  dismay, the crew
discovers that the women have been dead for centuries.  Kryten, the android
servant on the drifting ship, doesn't realize that the  crew has  died.  He
ends up joining the crew of the Red Dwarf and gets some lessons is slacking
off from Lister.  Rimmer studies a new language, Holly fiddles with music.

