Rimmer receives a letter from his mother, but cannot  read her handwriting.
Is his father "dad" or "dead"?  Did he pass away peacefully  in his "sleep"
or in a "jeep"?  The crew end up living out their dreams with the  aid of a
game "Better than Life" that arrives with the mail.

