The crew  on  board the  Red Dwarf  wakes up  one morning  to discover that
someone has erased their memories of the last four days.  Lister finds that
his leg  is  broken  and  is  in  a  cast, and  his jigsaw  puzzle has been
completed.  Rimmer  blames  the  problem  on  aliens.   The crew celebrates
Rimmer's deathday on a dead world.  Rimmer gets drunk.

